    {
      "bookmarkId": "23229251_1_294003-294034",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "294003-294034",
      "markText": "人生注定孤独，每个人都有自己的路要走，短暂的结伴终要面临分离。",
      "totalCount": 544,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23229251&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=294003&rangeEnd=294034",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/60732d30716273436078878?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=294003&rangeEnd=294034"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23229251_1_165957-166025",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "165957-166025",
      "markText": "我们生活的世界就是一头大象，众生就像盲人，围绕着这头巨象在乱摸，并把自己摸到的那一点当成是世界的真相。很少有人知道，亲身体验是有局限的。",
      "totalCount": 496,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23229251&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=165957&rangeEnd=166025",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/60732d30716273436078878?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=165957&rangeEnd=166025"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23229251_1_1017-1054",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "1017-1054",
      "markText": "这便是令西域和河西商人闻名丧胆的“莫贺延碛”，它还有一个名字，叫作流沙河。",
      "totalCount": 420,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23229251&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1017&rangeEnd=1054",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/60732d30716273436078878?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1017&rangeEnd=1054"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23229251_1_22516-22567",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "22516-22567",
      "markText": "对修行人来说，断食偏食都不适中，过分享乐和过分苦行都有偏颇。世间万事必须适中，过与不及都可能要坏事。”",
      "totalCount": 392,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23229251&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=22516&rangeEnd=22567",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/60732d30716273436078878?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=22516&rangeEnd=22567"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23229251_1_12-83",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "12-83",
      "markText": "这是个不可思议的地方，狂风裹挟着沙粒在空中飞舞，整个世界都变得混沌起来，如同天地初开时的景象。空气中弥漫着尖啸的声音，那是鬼魂们在不甘地号叫。",
      "totalCount": 360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23229251&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=12&rangeEnd=83",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/60732d30716273436078878?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=12&rangeEnd=83"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23229251_6_115600-115672",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "115600-115672",
      "markText": "佛教的最终追求并不是慈悲，而是智慧。一切修行都是为了获得终极智慧，所谓慈悲也是建立在智慧之上的慈悲，没有智慧的善是伪善，没有智慧的慈悲是假慈悲。",
      "totalCount": 352,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23229251&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=115600&rangeEnd=115672",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/60732d30716273436078878?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=115600&rangeEnd=115672"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23229251_1_290614-290671",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "290614-290671",
      "markText": "人心是一块田，不长庄稼，就会长草。这个世界上最大的不同就是人与人的不同，即使走着同一条路，心中的目的地也各不相同。",
      "totalCount": 351,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23229251&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=290614&rangeEnd=290671",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/60732d30716273436078878?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=290614&rangeEnd=290671"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23229251_8_269535-269624",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "269535-269624",
      "markText": "爱与尊重是很微妙的两种情绪，有时是此消彼长的状态——爱的多了，尊重就会少些；而尊重多了，爱就会少一点儿。人与人之间多数时候都是根据各自的地位和需求，在两者间取得一个微妙的平衡……",
      "totalCount": 345,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23229251&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=269535&rangeEnd=269624",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/60732d30716273436078878?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=269535&rangeEnd=269624"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23229251_1_51986-52025",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "51986-52025",
      "markText": "世人礼佛念佛，其实就是在礼自己的心，念自己的心，使自己道心坚固，并非心外求佛。",
      "totalCount": 330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23229251&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=51986&rangeEnd=52025",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/60732d30716273436078878?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=51986&rangeEnd=52025"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23229251_1_182979-182988",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "182979-182988",
      "markText": "佛不东来，我便西去",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23229251&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=182979&rangeEnd=182988",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/60732d30716273436078878?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=182979&rangeEnd=182988"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23229251_2_76906-76926",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "76906-76926",
      "markText": "“玄奘也不知，僧人的终点是自己的心灵。”",
      "totalCount": 304,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23229251&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=76906&rangeEnd=76926",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/60732d30716273436078878?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=76906&rangeEnd=76926"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23229251_1_6576-6603",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "6576-6603",
      "markText": "念念为自己，还是念念为众生，这便是凡夫与佛菩萨的区别！",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23229251&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=6576&rangeEnd=6603",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/60732d30716273436078878?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=6576&rangeEnd=6603"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23229251_4_228448-228535",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "228448-228535",
      "markText": "玄奘大概不会想到，一千多年后的2001年3月12日，在坦克和火箭炮以及数千吨TNT炸药的轰鸣声中，他曾亲眼见证亲笔记录下的大佛惨遭炸毁，尘土和硝烟弥漫了这片布满佛迹的山谷……",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23229251&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=228448&rangeEnd=228535",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/60732d30716273436078878?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=228448&rangeEnd=228535"
    },
    {
